{
  "id": "RAW_fbb37c",
  "title": "无损减少 80%激活值内存，提升 5 倍训练序列长度，仅需两行代码 ｜ 机器之心",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-06-23-9",
  "date": "2025-06-23 08:20:27",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:41\"><strong><br></strong></p>\n  <p><strong>本文的第一作者罗琪竣、第二作者李梦琦为香港中文大学（深圳）计算机科学博士生，本文在上海交通大学赵磊老师、香港中文大学（深圳）李肖老师的指导下完成。</strong></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:120\">长序列训练对于模型的长序列推理等能力至关重要。随着序列长度增加，训练所需储存的激活值快速增加，占据训练的大部分内存。即便使用梯度检查点（gradient checkpointing）方法，激活值依然占据大量内存，限制训练所能使用的序列长度。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:284\">来自港中文（深圳）和上海交通大学的团队提出 <strong>StreamBP </strong>算法。通过对链式法则进行线性分解和分步计算，StreamBP 将大语言模型训练所需的激活值内存（logits 和 layer activation）降低至梯度检查点（gradient checkpointing）的 20% 左右。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503491572\" data-ratio=\"0.9981481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4380de93-ef80-45a7-4b48-1a03c82bcb00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/6e0a7a9b-146d-4081-b866-83f5deacf942/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"3 4 []\" data-sourcepos=\"13:1-14:77\">论文标题：StreamBP: Memory-Efficient Exact Backpropagation for Long Sequence Training of LLMs</p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"3 4 []\" data-sourcepos=\"13:1-14:77\">论文：https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.03077</p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-sourcepos=\"13:1-14:77\">代码：https://github.com/Ledzy/StreamBP</p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:284\">在相同内存限制下，StreamBP 最大序列长度为梯度检查点的 2.8-5.5 倍。在相同序列长度下，StreamBP 的速度和梯度检查点接近甚至更快。StreamBP 适用于 SFT、GRPO、PPO 和 DPO 等常见 LLM 目标函数。代码已开源，可集成至现有训练代码。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"18:1-18:22\"><strong>激活值内存和梯度检查点</strong></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"20:1-20:87\">在反向传播（Backpropagation, BP）的过程中，计算模型梯度需要用到模型的中间输出（激活值）。举例来说，对于模型中的线性变换<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/606599e9-6b08-493c-3177-18ac29881e00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.20270270270270271\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"222\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491662\" data-original-style=\"width: 108px;height: 22px;\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3520815a-be5f-4518-8e05-5e07aee55912/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 14.34%;\">的梯度为<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c249ae85-0446-4978-d23c-83555419ee00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.2391304347826087\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"184\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491663\" data-original-style=\"width: 82px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4f248efd-ba38-416f-b171-93194e3549da/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 11.91%;\">，因而计算<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8119c3d7-5010-4450-bc92-610bfd4e7a00/public\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"39\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491700\" data-original-style=\"width:20px;height:20px;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/e74e4be0-d31c-47dd-8ba3-5536607d4e40/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 3.48%;\">的梯度时需要储存相应的激活值<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/105c98b2-a7c6-4fbc-76fa-48d4f1747b00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.8979591836734694\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"49\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491665\" data-original-style=\"width: 23px;height: 21px;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2d58405b-ed01-4ab5-893d-b8ce33c9ea01/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.22%;\">。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"22:1-24:223\">对于模型中的任意函数变换 <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/45674119-196d-429f-e88b-dad9239aef00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.2619047619047619\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"210\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491702\" data-original-style=\"width:104px;height:27px;\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5ed970b9-c365-47c2-b3eb-408890338406/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 13.28%;\">&nbsp;的梯度由以下链式法则计算：</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2d6ca5dd-581c-4e23-d91e-3b9ddccdc800/public\" data-ratio=\"0.1793103448275862\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"870\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gWicstpdJAkOm0xWuFVVbWT26s0tcCUGOibTHbBnvletlEBsMKx5qufjAnYm6iaGhd4Ss3lAJ5ZlYrzlQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"870\" data-cropy1=\"36.12456747404844\" data-cropy2=\"192.6643598615917\" data-imgfileid=\"503491577\" data-original-style=\"width: 578px;height: 104px;\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3c6aff8a-5884-4472-ac34-5f688391a7f5/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"22:1-24:223\">其中&nbsp;L&nbsp;为目标函数，<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf59e0e0-1694-4c41-7556-193af77ffb00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5258620689655172\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"116\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491666\" data-original-style=\"width: 58px;height: 31px;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/bf50ae9e-265d-4db1-8b69-d8fed41b0c7c/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 9.07%;\">为 Jacobian 矩阵。为了计算以上 Jacobian-vector product，需要在模型 forward 时储存函数变换<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bea4821e-3d84-4d58-2eb0-78686610bf00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"80\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491667\" data-original-style=\"width: 35px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/65afabae-ed4b-4002-b873-815ae110427a/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 6.01%;\">的中间值（激活值），其内存消耗与 batch size、序列长度以及中间值维度正相关。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"26:1-26:138\">为了减少激活值的内存消耗，梯度检查点（gradient checkpointing）方法在 forward 时只储存每一层网络的输入，而不储存该层的中间值。在 backward 至该层时，将重新 forward 此层输入来计算得到该层激活值。使用梯度检查点时储存的激活值包括：</p>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     <strong>所有层的输入</strong>，一般为激活值内存的 5%-15%。\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     <strong>单层的完整激活值</strong>，占据超过 85% 的激活值内存。\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"32:1-32:25\"><strong>StreamBP 的核心思想</strong></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"34:1-36:205\">不同于梯度检查点，StreamBP 避免储存单层的完整激活值，而将单层的 BP 过程进行线性分解，序列化计算并累加。注意到对于函数变换<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa08b165-a3f3-43fd-3c35-98dd5771f700/public\" data-ratio=\"0.1943127962085308\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"211\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491668\" data-original-style=\"width: 94px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/57f7abef-2de6-4a9e-8afd-cf9d3aa3d808/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 16.24%;\">，链式法则存在以下线性分解：</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/85f85385-975a-44bc-d8cb-8b668f52bc00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.11666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491582\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3ec24b0f-3275-4f0e-a70d-5636404baab5/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"34:1-36:205\">StreamBP 基于以下观察：对于 LLM 中的大部分函数变换<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4688895b-d468-41bb-f282-aaca6d2ffd00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5964912280701754\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"57\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gWicstpdJAkOm0xWuFVVbWT26jYbvglMYTjdksvfwweU7lAg9fxCwkXor1rtNJLGZPYTGIicYNqbwY4A/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"58\" data-cropy2=\"34\" data-imgfileid=\"503491583\" data-original-style=\"width: 38px;height: 23px;\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/df6ca58b-959d-4a77-b8f0-7c387e86b1f9/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.38%;\">，如 Transformer 层、lmhead 层，可通过策略性地将输出分块<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b5849710-2229-4783-fea4-da443ca4ca00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.18126888217522658\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"331\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491669\" data-original-style=\"width: 147px;height: 27px;\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8c83cd35-3dae-4369-927e-f1746c1ebe2b/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 23.41%;\">，使得计算块 Jacobian-vector product <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1bec8c4b-b2ad-413f-cf4f-86e0c723ed00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.35555555555555557\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"270\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491670\" data-original-style=\"width: 84px;height: 30px;\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2aa98e57-9947-4880-a88a-5ccb2515db01/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 18.13%;\">所需的激活值远小于计算完整的 Jacobian-vector product。基于该观察，StreamBP 依次计算上式中 D 个块的 Jacobian-vector product 并累加，得到准确的梯度。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"38:1-38:183\">为了计算块 Jacobian-vector product，需要分析<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bea4821e-3d84-4d58-2eb0-78686610bf00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"80\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491667\" data-original-style=\"width: 35px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/cdc92363-5023-4644-8a67-0a996e1b52fc/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 5.27%;\">输入和输出的相关性，每次 forward 块输入<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e32f98-6209-4069-6f4a-93ad5641b200/public\" data-ratio=\"0.9107142857142857\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"56\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491671\" data-original-style=\"width: 23px;height: 21px;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/07fa06b0-e3e6-4376-834e-782b221f012f/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.43%;\"> 得到块输出<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c0aaa3b-3da9-48f6-e83b-d5025d501700/public\" data-ratio=\"0.84375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491672\" data-original-style=\"width: 27px;height: 23px;\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0bede28c-8176-4e48-ab55-20eb8e5dd20c/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"17\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.96%;\">，建立对应子计算图。以简单的线性变换<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc54b49f-976f-4d8d-9db1-a5cb3ce25a00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.20416666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"240\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491673\" data-original-style=\"width: 106px;height: 22px;\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/6a71fff8-8952-4b29-9b76-8b1cbd8f26c1/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 17.08%;\">&nbsp;为例，输出和输入在行维度上一一对应。StreamBP 按行分块，每次计算单行的 Jacobian-vector product 并累加。下图对比了标准 BP 和 StreamBP 在上述线性变换下的实现：</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/99321ebd-ebf6-4e4a-aee7-e4aaf80b1b00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.2759259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491593\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ca039500-ab9d-45a4-b2a4-bb99c6be628c/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"19\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"42:1-42:94\">D 步累加得到的<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bec5b4e6-e986-4abb-22ff-5e0bcac26400/public\" data-ratio=\"0.875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"40\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491675\" data-original-style=\"width: 20px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"21\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/227b4fea-c980-4d8d-8644-89549a13c168/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.01%;\">和<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2b80ab27-ede9-463c-3eae-bb28dacb9700/public\" data-ratio=\"0.7954545454545454\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"44\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491678\" data-original-style=\"width: 22px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"22\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/33518850-e997-4813-9c1d-57f3b2e6cccf/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"21\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.32%;\">即为<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d0d7bb01-4dd2-449f-234a-2e08fa58a200/public\" data-ratio=\"0.7222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"54\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491679\" data-original-style=\"width: 24px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"23\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/22aa01c8-0693-48b0-93c5-8415d7db147d/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"23\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.01%;\">和<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/79008a9c-44c0-4960-b467-f42fa67a2200/public\" data-ratio=\"0.8076923076923077\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"52\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491680\" data-original-style=\"width: 22px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"24\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/afc4cd87-57f5-436c-969d-a49966c4cb14/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"22\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 3.69%;\">准确梯度。相比于标准 BP，StreamBP 仅需储存<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/115326a6-762b-43a2-4691-d04a7303c700/public\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"40\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491681\" data-original-style=\"width: 20px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"25\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a4d57ccb-50b5-48f3-9769-254ab4748c60/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"24\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 3.37%;\">和<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fa7d19c1-7724-41b9-167a-d07a2911b500/public\" data-ratio=\"0.8076923076923077\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"52\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491682\" data-original-style=\"width: 25px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"26\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/48a3c1ec-349f-489e-918f-172205569c77/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"25\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.11%;\">，且总计算 FLOPs 相同。下表为 StreamBP 和标准 BP 的内存和时间对比：</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503491616\" data-ratio=\"0.23703703703703705\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b87d7700-75eb-4b78-2c8e-78968cb14800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"27\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/34cea025-0a15-4a23-8b7a-7733d1d0899b/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"26\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"48:1-48:28\"><strong>LLM 训练中的 StreamBP</strong></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"50:1-50:69\">StreamBP 应用于 LLM 中的 Transformer 层和 lmhead 层，分别用于降低层激活值和 logits 的内存消耗。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"52:1-52:93\">与线性变换不同，由于 Transformer 层存在注意力机制，块输出<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c1d1c2e-aba6-4557-ec00-982f0ae60d00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491684\" data-original-style=\"width: 31px;height: 25px;\" data-index=\"28\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ffc0675f-d90a-4829-b4f2-070375a7bd85/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"30\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.74%;\">并非仅由对应位置的块输入<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47544045-9255-4c74-7bc7-1fae1422d400/public\" data-ratio=\"0.847457627118644\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"59\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491685\" data-original-style=\"width: 23px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"29\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/93734ad7-2599-461f-b337-0ecc9427520b/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"27\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.64%;\">决定，而与该块及以前所有位置的输入<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b72b58cf-66e7-4d3d-1e63-9bb6b54bfc00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.19242902208201892\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"317\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491686\" data-original-style=\"width: 129px;height: 25px;\" data-index=\"30\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/874d08c0-6c64-481c-a1c6-cef886724529/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"28\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 23.41%;\">都有关。StreamBP 利用<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c1d1c2e-aba6-4557-ec00-982f0ae60d00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491684\" data-original-style=\"width: 25px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"31\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/04e9abeb-b6f4-4f74-8bcc-dda002062db1/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"29\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 4.43%;\">只与块<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/40cf4b00-8fab-4786-5621-e52d48878c00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.23529411764705882\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"187\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491687\" data-original-style=\"width: 80px;height: 20px;\" data-index=\"32\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d3d1c899-2674-413e-a2eb-22d7a9df9906/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"31\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 16.24%;\">有关的性质，建立了如下计算图：</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/56ccf3d8-4ca3-455e-99e6-3b92a1247200/public\" data-ratio=\"0.35648148148148145\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491634\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"33\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7fa9f8b3-bc52-4bf1-b4c1-dd8a5d3e4aa3/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"32\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"56:1-56:48\">StreamBP 所需储存的激活值和注意力掩码（橙色）大幅低于梯度检查点（橙色 + 白色部分）。</p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"58:1-58:125\">对于 lmhead 层，当以 SFT 或 GRPO 为目标函数时，观察到不同位置的 logits 对于目标函数的影响相互独立。因此，StreamBP 从序列维度分块，每次计算单块损失函数的梯度，从而只需储存单块 logits 和 logits 梯度。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503491635\" data-ratio=\"0.2384169884169884\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ae52bf84-5c13-45a9-fae7-c33d5c988b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1036\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"34\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b12eb1e8-ebef-4b5a-8c77-2599af4f6635/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"33\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"60:1-60:18\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图：StreamBP for SFT</sup></p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/87ec9e42-5281-48ae-5e35-34af0a10f000/public\" data-ratio=\"0.36574074074074076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491636\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"35\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/966e3b37-1e68-4336-a1e3-76003e81b572/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"34\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"62:1-62:19\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图：StreamBP for GRPO</sup></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"64:1-64:94\">对于 DPO，由于非线性 sigmoid 函数的存在，每个位置的 logits 对于目标函数的影响并不独立。StreamBP 利用 logits 梯度在序列维度的独立性，分块进行梯度计算。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503491637\" data-ratio=\"0.36203703703703705\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/68dce542-7038-48de-faa4-8ae03e545900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"36\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7eb76f5f-5f14-47a1-ab61-3f1d0a7f8dfd/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"35\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"66:1-66:18\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图：StreamBP for DPO</sup></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"70:1-70:15\"><strong>实验结果</strong></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"72:1-72:86\">我们在单张 A800-80GB GPU 上测试了不同大小的模型，StreamBP 的最大 BP 序列长度为标准 BP 的 23-36 倍，梯度检查点的 2.5-5.5 倍。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503491638\" data-ratio=\"0.31666666666666665\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/30756b95-27a1-49c8-8f27-69b115492d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"37\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/754dd40f-4dfc-4bd8-95bf-305f28517212/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"36\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"74:1-74:21\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图：不同序列长度下的 BP 峰值内存</sup></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"76:1-76:99\">在现有 Transformers 框架下，StreamBP 的实现可避免计算掩码部分的 pre-attention score（见论文 3.2.2 部分），在长序列训练下相较于梯度检查点实现了加速。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b1ac6a0a-8a34-4375-80f5-5a3226820e00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.28888888888888886\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491639\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"38\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/819bc14b-7af7-4ccd-b942-97588be26a64/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"37\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"78:1-78:71\">通过使用 StreamBP，不同目标函数下最大的序列长度得到了大幅提升。在同样的序列长度下，StreamBP 允许更大的批处理大小以加速训练。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35c79ff8-fa4a-44f5-e04a-f2ce02f9cf00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.39814814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491640\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"39\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/48cb449e-80f1-4906-afda-a867d2fea3df/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"38\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc5e0b2e-5916-4caa-457c-fb8bd4edb300/public\" data-ratio=\"0.2773279352226721\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"988\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491641\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"40\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a3ae273c-9ea5-4c7e-8ae5-4d2f68120377/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"39\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"80:1-80:34\"><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 表：Qwen 3-4B 单个样本 BP 时间，序列长度为 9000。</sup></p>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"82:1-82:65\">在 Deepspeed ZeRO 分布式训练模式下，Distributed StreamBP 比梯度检查点的最大可训练序列长度提升了5—5.6倍。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23ac8cef-0c28-4f51-78bb-f8c1064adf00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.17222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503491642\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"41\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/accba7aa-b091-4293-b386-094d585f1d9e/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"40\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "StreamBP 算法无损减少大模型 80%激活值内存，大幅提升长序列训练能力，代码已开源。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "StreamBP 算法无损减少大模型 80%激活值内存，大幅提升长序列训练能力，代码已开源。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了一种名为 StreamBP 的新型反向传播算法，旨在解决大语言模型（LLM）长序列训练中激活值内存占用过高的问题。该算法通过对链式法则进行线性分解，并策略性地将输出分块进行分步序列化计算，避免了储存单层完整的激活值，从而将训练所需的激活值内存降低至传统梯度检查点方法的约 20%。实验结果表明，在相同的内存限制下，StreamBP 可将最大训练序列长度提升 2.8-5.5 倍（单卡）至 5-5.6 倍（分布式），且速度与梯度检查点相当或更快。StreamBP 适用于 SFT、GRPO、PPO、DPO 等多种主流 LLM 训练目标函数，并已开源代码，易于集成到现有训练框架中，为 LLM 的高效长序列训练提供了关键优化方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "StreamBP 通过分解反向传播过程大幅减少激活值内存",
      "explanation": "它将链式法则线性分解并分步计算，避免储存单层完整激活值，将内存降至梯度检查点的 20%，显著缓解内存瓶颈。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该方法显著提升了大语言模型长序列训练能力",
      "explanation": "在相同内存下，StreamBP 最大序列长度可达梯度检查点的 2.8-5.6 倍，解锁更长上下文训练，提升模型表现。"
    },
    {
      "point": "StreamBP 易于集成并适用于多种主流训练目标",
      "explanation": "代码已开源且可集成至现有训练框架，支持 SFT/GRPO/PPO/DPO 等，应用广泛，降低使用门槛。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "即便使用梯度检查点（gradient checkpointing）方法，激活值依然占据大量内存，限制训练所能使用的序列长度。",
    "StreamBP 将大语言模型训练所需的激活值内存（logits 和 layer activation）降低至梯度检查点（gradient checkpointing）的 20% 左右。",
    "在相同内存限制下，StreamBP 最大序列长度为梯度检查点 的 2.8-5.5 倍。",
    "StreamBP 适用于 SFT、GRPO、PPO 和 DPO 等常见 LLM 目标函数。代码已开源，可集成至现有训练代码。"
  ],
